parameters:
The old man in the field hurt his back. I guess it can't be helped
since he's already getting old.

He asked me to watch the field for him, but it doesn't seem like
anything out of the ordinary.

Sigh... I've been so busy lately that I haven't had a chance to talk
with \n[1] slowly.
I understand that \n[1] is doing his best because of Light, but...
I wonder when my feelings will reach \n[1].
Hey! Hasn't this kind of pattern been happening a lot lately!?
In the blink of an eye, the tentacles entwined around my whole body.

However, even though \n[1] isn't nearby this time, we're still in the
village. If I call for help, someone will come running to assist.

At the moment I tried to call for help, I felt like I heard a voice
asking for help from somewhere.

I'm not sure, but it seems like the voice is coming from this thing in
front of me.
...What's going on? It hurts and help me...

I think others can probably hear it normally. Are you aware that
you're speaking?
Is that a distress call...? It might not be good!
Please help me, I can't hold on any longer...
Please help me, I can't hold on any longer...
It's become difficult to eat properly lately.
We are on the verge of dying just like this...
Lately... is this field also being affected by the curse?
I don't think she's lying, but what should I do?

I found you at such a time. Why are you sparkling and exuding such a
powerful aura?

Could you please refrain from emitting that kind of aura for just a
little while?
It's fine if you can share your nutrients with us.
Is there any connection between that and the current situation?
Yes! I'm receiving nutrients from your body, thank you very much.

I finally understand that the previous attack by the plant monsters
was probably caused by this.
Ugh, it's just for this time, okay?
Thank you very much! You are our source of nutrients!

I understand! The boss of the field, who responded, slowly began to
move its tentacles.
Delicious! It's delicious! But... What should I call you?
That's right! Since I'm receiving nutrients from your body...!
Is that how it is? I'm called Miiru, isn't that a nice name?
Miiru, is it? What a splendid name!

I wouldn't mind if you said it like that. You don't have to use
honorifics, just call me Miiru.
Thank you very much! You are our source of nutrients!
It feels a little strange when you speak brokenly, but that's fine.

While having such a nonsensical conversation, the tentacles were
slithering all over my body.

I felt slimy from the beginning, but it seems like the intensity has
increased somehow.
I wonder if this is really going to save him.

It might just feel like a regular meal, but I'm starting to feel
strange little by little.
That makes me feel somewhat uneasy.
Why do you look so comfortable too?!

I... I'm sorry, Miiru-chan. It felt so delicious that I ended up
feeling a strange sensation.
I wonder if that's just how it is.
Miiru-chan, I also feel a strange sensation when I'm with you...
It's not like I'm feeling good or anything... hah\i[249]

Suddenly, tentacles are forcefully pressing against my genitals...
Does this guy know what he's doing?

I... I'm sorry, Miiru-chan. It felt so delicious that I ended up
feeling a strange sensation.

I want to find out where your sweet secret is hidden... I want to keep
sucking it out like this...

The movements of the tentacles suddenly became more unsettling, and
the slime is dripping out vigorously.

I think the tentacles trembled and then liquid sprayed out from the
tip.

There's obviously no escape for me, and I end up being showered all
over my body.

I've been feeling a little strange for a while now, but for some
reason, when I touch this slimy thing, my head feels fuzzy.

It's like bathing in that sweet, sweet syrup all over my body, and a
feeling of happiness wells up within me.
No... I'm getting really excited. At this rate...
Haa... haa... this is the best... *gulp gulp*
...I'm tired from eating a lot, so I'm going to sleep.
Well, it seems like you're satisfied, so I guess it's fine...
What am I supposed to do, being the only one left!

I'm going to enter from the next door to the tool shop. I'm not here
to play today.
I came to buy some items, you know!
Enter the door right next to us.
